-appetit">BON APPÉTIT</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/conde-nast-johansens">CONDÉ NAST JOHANSENS</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/conde-nast-traveler">CONDÉ NAST TRAVELER</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/epicurious">EPICURIOUS</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/glamour">GLAMOUR</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/gq">GQ</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/house-garden">HOUSE &amp; GARDEN</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/la-cucina-italiana">LA CUCINA ITALIANA</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/love">LOVE</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/pitchfork">PITCHFORK</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/self">SELF</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/tatler">TATLER</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2f3e pb-1"><a class="font-small pb-2 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300" href="/brands/teen-vogue">TEEN VOGUE</a></div><div class="jsx-d4ca4a36817c2